<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Non-Exhaustive on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/non-exhaustive/</link><description>Recent content in Non-Exhaustive on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/non-exhaustive/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Non-exhaustive patterns</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/non-exhaustive/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/non-exhaustive/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;Non-exhaustive patterns&lt;/code&gt; warning (which becomes a runtime error) occurs when a function&amp;rsquo;s pattern matching doesn&amp;rsquo;t cover all possible input values. The compiler may warn about this with &lt;code&gt;-Wincomplete-patterns&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing cases for data constructors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Not handling empty lists&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing catch-all patterns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incomplete guards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-haskell" data-lang="haskell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- WARNING: Non-exhaustive patterns in function &amp;#39;tail&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;safeTail&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; [a] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; [a]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;safeTail&lt;/span&gt; (x&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;xs) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; xs
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Missing: safeTail [] = []&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- CORRECT: Add all cases&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;safeTail&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; [a] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; [a]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;safeTail&lt;/span&gt; (x&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;xs) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; xs
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;safeTail&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-haskell" data-lang="haskell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- WARNING: Non-exhaustive pattern&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;describe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Bool&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;describe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;True&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;yes&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Missing: describe False = &amp;#34;no&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- CORRECT: Cover all constructors&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;describe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Bool&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;describe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;True&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;yes&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;describe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;False&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;no&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-haskell" data-lang="haskell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Example 1: Missing list case&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;head&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; (x&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; x
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- head&amp;#39; [] crashes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Example 2: Missing Bool case&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;not&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;True&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;False&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- not&amp;#39; False crashes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Example 3: Missing Maybe case&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fromJust&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Just&lt;/span&gt; x) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; x
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- fromJust Nothing crashes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/pattern-match"&gt;Pattern match failure&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/variable-not-in-scope"&gt;Variable not in scope&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Pattern match failure</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/pattern-match/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/pattern-match/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A pattern match failure occurs when a function encounters a value that none of its pattern matching cases handle. Haskell throws an &lt;code&gt;IrrefutablePatternFailed&lt;/code&gt; exception at runtime.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incomplete pattern on lists&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing Maybe/Either cases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guards that reject all values&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Case expression without catch-all&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-haskell" data-lang="haskell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- WRONG: Incomplete pattern on lists&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;headSafe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; [a] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; a
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;headSafe&lt;/span&gt; (x&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;xs) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; x
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Missing: headSafe [] = error &amp;#34;empty list&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- CORRECT: Add missing cases&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;headSafe&lt;/span&gt; (x&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;xs) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; x
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;headSafe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;empty list&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-haskell" data-lang="haskell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- WRONG: Missing Maybe case&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fromMaybe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt; a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Maybe&lt;/span&gt; a &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; a
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fromMaybe&lt;/span&gt; def (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Just&lt;/span&gt; x) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; x
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Missing: fromMaybe def Nothing = def&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- CORRECT: Handle all cases&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fromMaybe&lt;/span&gt; def (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Just&lt;/span&gt; x) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; x
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fromMaybe&lt;/span&gt; def &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Nothing&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; def
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-haskell" data-lang="haskell"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Example 1: Incomplete list pattern&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;headSafe&lt;/span&gt; (x&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;_&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; x
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;headSafe&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;error&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;empty&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Calling headSafe [] still crashes if not caught&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Example 2: Missing Maybe case&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;unwrap&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Just&lt;/span&gt; x) &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; x
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Calling unwrap Nothing crashes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Example 3: Guard rejects all&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;classify&lt;/span&gt; n
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; n &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;positive&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; n &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;negative&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- classify 0 crashes (no otherwise)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/non-exhaustive"&gt;Non-exhaustive patterns&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/haskell/infinite-loop"&gt;Infinite loop / stack overflow&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>